channel.title: Turkey That Tastes Like Fish?
channel.description:
Turkey That Tastes Like Fish?
Yoza. This morning, I shot a 10kg turkey with my .22 Air Rifle(5 Pumps) from 10 metres away, it died instantly, at my dads run off. Now, when we ate it tonight, it tasted like fish.... Is this normal/safe?
